{"tid":796492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】最新消息：傳郭炳湘深夜心臟病發暈倒送院","createTime":"2018-08-27T21:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T10:13:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":99,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"b476a979885fb909eb3430d49366f2314948bdec","tid":796492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T21:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535392720_6b2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535392720_6b2b.jpg&h=29e20942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島深水灣道新地郭家大宅，昨晚11時48分，大宅內一名姓郭67歲男子突感覺不適，由救護員送院治理，經搶救後留醫治理，警方列作有人暈倒案件處理。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，送院男子為新地郭氏家族長子郭炳湘，據知他上周曾外遊，近期返港，至昨晚疑因心臟病發不適送院，數名親友趕至醫院探望，郭經搶救後被推出急症室，記者上前採訪期間，被疑似郭近身保鑣從後扯開，手提電話脫手墮地，郭被送往醫院，留醫心臟及深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535393712_1b95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535393712_1b95.jpg&h=6f3a79c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者拍攝時被保鑣阻止。(李家傑攝)"},{"pid":"789eaa0fc00aa4a0cf6e8009598031b6e5597f15","tid":796492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T21:03:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180828/58615107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F58615107&d=f3VJkYOrhkK6zum4%2Byswhtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8996e9f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F58615107&h=2281cab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180828/58615107</a>"},{"pid":"520e5b0e02650e9e2401035bc8fda0f66e416229","tid":796492,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime